      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/ac/sqa-level2-pedicle-fea",
      "rationale": "The FEA software (Ansys Mechanical 2021 R1) operates under an ISO 9001-certified quality management system. Version control, regression testing, and change control procedures are documented in the vendor's software quality plan. The required level of 2 reflects that the model risk level is 3 and the COU is a medium-consequence regulatory submission; achieving level 3 provides additional margin. Acceptance criterion: documented SQA plan with evidence of version-controlled solver benchmarks."
