      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/ac/ncv-level2-pedicle-fea",
      "rationale": "Solver verification confirmed via NAFEMS benchmark suite LE1 and LE10 for linear static structural analysis. Results agree within 0.5% of analytical solutions. Required level 2 is consistent with medium model risk and established commercial solver usage in orthopedic device FEA submissions. Acceptance criterion: NAFEMS benchmark pass rate ≥99% for applicable test cases."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
