      "rationale": "Validation activities directly replicate the COU: same device geometry, same material lot, same ASTM F1717 test protocol, same QoIs. The validation domain is considered representative of the intended use domain with no extrapolation required. Required level 3 is consistent with medium model risk and the regulatory context. Acceptance criterion: validation scenario matches COU on all five relevance dimensions (geometry, material, loading, environment, QoI) as documented in the relevance assessment matrix."
