    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted despite Test conditions factor achieving level 2 against a required level of 3. The shortfall is mitigated by the high relevance of the single validated condition to the COU, the quantitative output comparison results (all E/uval < 1.96), and the medium model influence classification. The remaining 12 factors meet or exceed required levels. The credibility evidence package is deemed sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct.",
